---
import Blog from "@layouts/blog";
import { toKebabCase } from "../utils/helper"

const howdyComponent = [
  {
    title: 'Animation Dialog',
    text: '使用动画打开模态框',
    link: ''
  },
  {
    title: 'Resize',
    text: '为HTML盒子加入拖拽更改大小功能'
  },
  {
    title: 'Scroll',
    text: '为HTML盒子加入自定义滚动条'
  },
  {
    title: 'Size Observer',
    text: '监听盒子大小变化'
  },
  {
    title: 'Img Zoom',
    text: '为Img标签加入图片放大功能，支持按组浏览下一张图片'
  },
  {
    title: 'To Drag',
    text: '为Fixed定位的元素加入可拖拽功能'
  },
  {
    title: 'Standard Tabs',
    text: '移动端标签页'
  },
  {
    title: 'Mouse Menu',
    text: '自定义右键菜单'
  },
  {
    title: 'To Control',
    text: '将元素设置为可拖拽改变位置与大小'
  }
].map(item => {
  let linkText = toKebabCase(item.title)
  item.link = `https://kongfandong.cn/howdy/${linkText}`
  return item
})

const howdyLink = [
  {
    name: '⚡ Github',
    link: 'https://github.com/leon-kfd/howdyjs/'
  },
  {
    name: '📖 Document',
    link: 'https://kongfandong.cn/howdy/'
  },
  {
    name: '💾 NPM',
    link: 'https://www.npmjs.com/search?q=%40howdyjs'
  }
]

const dashboardLink = [
  {
    name: '⚡ Github',
    link: 'https://github.com/leon-kfd/Dashboard/'
  },
  {
    name: '📖 Document',
    link: 'https://doc.howdz.xyz'
  },
  {
    name: '🌈 Live Demo',
    link: 'https://howdz.xyz'
  }
]

const coderLink = [
  {
    name: '⚡ Github',
    link: 'https://github.com/leon-kfd/OnlineCodeEditor'
  },
  {
    name: '📖 Article',
    link: 'https://kongfandong.cn/blog/record-for-online-code-editor/'
  },
  {
    name: '🌈 Live Demo',
    link: 'https://s.kongfandong.cn'
  }
]

const musicVisualizerLink = [
  {
    name: '⚡ Github',
    link: 'https://github.com/leon-kfd/g-music-visualizer'
  },
  {
    name: '📖 Article',
    link: 'https://kongfandong.cn/blog/g-music-visualizer/'
  },
  {
    name: '🌈 Live Demo',
    link: 'https://leon-kfd.github.io/g-music-visualizer/'
  }
]

const scriptableLink = [
  {
    name: '⚡ Github',
    link: 'https://github.com/leon-kfd/howdy-scriptable'
  },
  {
    name: '📖 Document',
    link: 'https://scriptable.deno.dev/'
  }
]

const howdzImgLine = [
  {
    name: '📖 Document',
    link: 'https://i.howdz.xyz'
  },
]

---

<Blog title="Project" isPage>
  <h2 class="mt-10 uppercase title-decoration">Latest</h2>
  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.6em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://kongfandong.cn/howdz/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Howdz 🔸 浏览器起始页
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {dashboardLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      完全自定义配置的浏览器导航首页面板，支持自定义添加天气、时钟、搜索、收藏等各种物料组件，可编辑删除组件与其各种样式或功能属性。响应式设计，可自定义随机壁纸背景图或动态壁纸。
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.6em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://kongfandong.cn/howdy/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Howdyjs 🔸 插件库
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {howdyLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      个人JS插件库，包含自定义拖拽、滚动条、右键菜单、图片放大等原生JS插件和动画模态框、标签页等Vue3组件或指令。
    </div>
    <details>
      <summary>组件列表</summary>
      <ul class="howdy-component">
        {
          howdyComponent.map(item =>
            <li>
              <a href={item.link} target="_blank">{item.title}</a>
              <p>{item.text}</p>
            </li>
          )
        }
      </ul>
    </details>
  </section>

  <h2 class="mt-10 uppercase title-decoration">Other</h2>

  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.6em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://i.howdz.xyz`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        🎲 Howdz Image Service - 图片服务
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {howdzImgLine.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      基于<code>Vercel Edge function</code>实现的一个云函数图片服务，提供随机返回电影台词海报、随机古诗海报、生成二维码等图片服务，API可支持配置多个参数生成图片。
    </div>
    <details>
      <summary>图片服务预览</summary>
      <ul class="howdy-component">
        <li>
          <p>Movie Lines</p>
          <a href="https://i.howdz.xyz" target="_blank">
            <img src="https://i.howdz.xyz/api/movie?w=300&no-cache=1" loading="lazy" style="box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,.25)"/>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>Sentence</p>
          <a href="https://i.howdz.xyz" target="_blank">
            <img src="https://i.howdz.xyz/api/sentence?w=300&no-cache=1" loading="lazy" style="box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,.25)"/>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p>QRCode</p>
          <a href="https://i.howdz.xyz" target="_blank">
            <img src="https://i.howdz.xyz/api/qrcode?data=https%253A%252F%252Fhowdz.xyz&w=256&auto-icon=1" loading="lazy" style="box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,.25)"/>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </details>
  </section>

  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.6em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://kongfandong.cn/coder/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        💻 Code Editor - 在线代码IDE
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {coderLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      基于Vue3实现的一个仿<code>CodePen</code>的在线代码IDE，响应式布局支持移动端，可拖拽更改页面布局。另支持<code>Sass</code>语法、<code>Emmet</code>快输、自动刷新等。
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.6em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://leon-kfd.github.io/g-music-visualizer/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        🎵 Music Visualizer - 音乐可视化方案
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {musicVisualizerLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      利用<code>G</code>渲染器与React制作的一个音乐可视化方案，基于AudioContext的decodeAudioDataAPI读取音频数据，可以随机获取一首歌曲体验多种可视化效果。
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.6em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://scriptable.deno.dev/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        📱 Scriptable - IOS小组件
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {scriptableLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      使用<code>Scriptable</code>编写IOS小组件，当前包含随机电影台词、随机古诗、随机英文句子、掘金热榜等脚本，以上脚本会同时包含随机背景图定时刷新展示。
    </div>
  </section>
</Blog>
